Faster quick quick quick

1894
02:26:38,743 --> 02:26:39,973
What's going on here?

1895
02:26:43,732 --> 02:26:44,288
Quick

1896
02:26:49,763 --> 02:26:51,891
Get out. Quick quick quick. Out.

1897
02:26:53,248 --> 02:26:59,711
