02:34:58,093 --> 02:34:59,874
Seelenfreund, Estella

2001
02:35:14,479 --> 02:35:15,446
Run faster.

2002
02:35:15,566 --> 02:35:17,777
Run faster. Faster.

2003
02:35:17,836 --> 02:35:20,373
Faster. Faster. Come on. Forward.

2004
02:35:21,681 --> 02:35:24,084
Go on. Go on. Go on. Faster.

2005
02:35:27,519 --> 02:35:28,682
Faster. Move.

2006
02:35:31,798 --> 02:35:33,363
Scare them. Scare them.

2007
02:35:38,998 --> 02:35:41,914
No no no

2008
02:35:44,420 --> 02:35:48,110
Girl, let's go now. Now, quickly.

2009
02:35:59,357 --> 02:36:02,806
Danka Danka Danka

2010
02:36:02,878 --> 02:36:05,200
No no no

2011
02:36:07,289 --> 02:36:10,884
Hey hey hey. What are you doing?

2012
02:36:11,277 --> 02:36:14,878
These are mine. These
are my workers. They should be on my train.

2013
02:36:15,837 --> 02:36:18,039
They're skilled
munitions workers. They're essential

2014
02:36:18,876 --> 02:36:20,057
essential girls.

2015
02:36:23,595 --> 02:36:27,240
Their fingers
polish the insides of shell metal casings.

2016
02:36:27,932 --> 02:36:29,537
How else am I to polish the inside

2017
02:36:29,595 --> 02:36:31,160
of a 45 millimetre shell casing?

2018
02:36:31,356 --> 02:36:33,298
You tell me. You tell me.

2019
02:36:36,235 --> 02:36:37,381
Back on the train.

2020
02:36:38,769 --> 02:36:39,742
Back on the train.

2021
02:38:29,990 --> 02:38:32,839
Under Department W provisions

2022
02:38:33,950 --> 02:38:36,754
it is unlawful
to kill a worker without just cause.

2023
02:38:38,271 --> 02:38:40,670
Under the Businesses Compensation Fund

2024
02:38:41,269 --> 02:38:43,997
I am entitled
to file damage claims for such deaths.

2025
02:38:45,465 --> 02:38:47,626
If you shoot without thinking

2026
02:38:48,429 --> 02:38:49,445
you go to prison

2027
02:38:50,704 --> 02:38:51,575
I get paid.

2028
02:38:52,628 --> 02:38:53,485
That's how it works.

2029
02:38:54,828 --> 02:38:55,366
So

2030
02:38:56,223 --> 02:38:58,454
there will be no summary executions here.

2031
02:39:00,628 --> 02:39:03,673
There will be
no interference of any kind with production.

2032
02:39:05,268 --> 02:39:06,444
In hopes of ensuring that,

2033
02:39:07,019 --> 02:39:09,749
guards will
no longer be allowed on the factory floor

2034
02:39:10,227 --> 02:39:11,918
without my authorization.

2035
02:39:18,409 --> 02:39:20,839
For your cooperation you have my gratitude.

2036
02:39:23,360 --> 02:39:24,492
Come on. Come.

2037
02:39:25,989 --> 02:39:27,875
Man! I haven't seen such a thing for years.

2038
02:39:27,987 --> 02:39:29,333
Come on, boys. Come.

2039
02:39:29,390 --> 02:39:31,175
Look at the men.

2040
02:39:55,744 --> 02:39:56,685
No doorman

2041
02:39:57,543 --> 02:40:00,003
or maitre d' will ever mistake you again.

2042
02:40:01,388 --> 02:40:02,146
I promise.

2043
02:40:07,409 --> 02:40:07,954
Itzhak

2044
02:40:10,237 --> 02:40:11,977
This is Itzhak Stern, my accountant. Itzhak

2045
02:40:12,035 --> 02:40:13,649
You must be Mrs. Schindler.

2046
02:40:13,744 --> 02:40:14,566
It's a pleasure to meet you.

2047
02:40:14,676 --> 02:40:16,246
Emilie has volunteered to work in the clinic.

2048
02:40:16,304 --> 02:40:18,116
- Very generous of you.
- I know.

2049
02:40:18,173 --> 02:40:19,664
We need to talk when you have a moment.

2050
02:40:20,944 --> 02:40:23,227
This is my wife, Stern.
I don't keep any secrets from my spouse.

2051
02:40:23,287 --> 02:40:25,848
Oskar, please, attend
to business. It's much more attractive.

2052
02:40:26,387 --> 02:40:27,371
- Madam
- Hello

2053
02:40:27,431 --> 02:40:29,203
- What is it?
- We've received an angry complaint

2054
02:40:29,262 --> 02:40:30,347
from the Armaments Board.

2055
02:40:30,944 --> 02:40:32,985
The artillery shells,
tank shells, rocket casings

2056
02:40:33,063 --> 02:40:35,565
apparently all of them
have failed quality control tests.

2057
02:40:35,623 --> 02:40:37,471
That's to be expected: start-up problems.

2058
02:40:37,664 --> 02:40:39,803
This isn't
pots and pans. This is a precise business.

2059
02:40:39,862 --> 02:40:41,644
- I'll write them a letter.
- They're withholding payment.

2060
02:40:41,702 --> 02:40:43,468
Sure. So would I. So would you.

2061
02:40:43,543 --> 02:40:45,806
I wouldn't worry about it.
We'll get it right one of these days.

2062
02:40:45,862 --> 02:40:48,771
There's a rumour, you've been
going around miscalibrating the machines.

2063
02:40:50,423 --> 02:40:52,735
They could
shut us down and send us back to Auschwitz.

2064
02:40:55,824 --> 02:40:57,907
I'll call around
and find out where we can buy shells

2065
02:40:58,044 --> 02:40:58,874
and pass them off as ours.

2066
02:40:58,932 --> 02:40:59,956
I don't see the difference

2067
02:41:00,015 --> 02:41:01,268
whether they're made here or somewhere else

2068
02:41:01,327 --> 02:41:02,804
You
don't see a difference? I see a difference.

2069
02:41:02,862 --> 02:41:03,709
You'll lose a lot of money.

2070
02:41:03,766 --> 02:41:05,021
Fewer shells will be made.

2071
02:41:05,718 --> 02:41:07,443
Stern, if this factory ever produces

2072
02:41:07,503 --> 02:41:09,043
a shell that can actually be fired

2073
02:41:09,432 --> 02:41:10,637
I'll be very unhappy.

2074
02:41:12,541 --> 02:41:14,440
- Hello, madam
- How do you do.

2075
02:41:28,543 --> 02:41:29,459
How are you doing, Rabbi?

2076
02:41:30,691 --> 02:41:31,380
Rabbi

2077
02:41:34,822 --> 02:41:35,997
Good, Herr Direktor

2078
02:41:38,482 --> 02:41:39,444
The sun's going down.

2079
02:41:42,863 --> 02:41:43,987
Yes, it is.

2080
02:41:46,113 --> 02:41:46,852
What day is this?

2081
02:41:47,449 --> 02:41:48,008
Friday?

2082
02:41:48,579 --> 02:41:49,587
It is Friday, isn't it?

2083
02:41:49,892 --> 02:41:50,459
Is it?

2084
02:41:55,262 --> 02:41:56,381
What's the matter with you?

2085
02:41:56,912 --> 02:41:58,673
You should be preparing for the sabbath

2086
02:42:00,012 --> 02:42:00,765
shouldn't you?

2087
02:42:08,661 --> 02:42:09,717
I've got some wine

2088
02:42:10,963 --> 02:42:12,363
in my office. Come.

2089
02:43:25,072 --> 02:43:25,647
What?

2090
02:43:28,069 --> 02:43:29,097
Do you have any money

2091
02:43:31,552 --> 02:43:34,031
hidden away
some place that I don't know about?

2092
02:43:38,730 --> 02:43:39,203
No

2093
02:43:45,376 --> 02:43:46,893
Why? Am I broke?

2094
02:43:49,294 --> 02:43:50,031
Uh

2095
02:43:52,039 --> 02:43:52,883
well...

2096
02:43:55,175 --> 02:43:56,668
<i>Yesterday morning</i>

2097
02:43:57,388 --> 02:44:00,230
<i>at 2:41 a.m.</i>

2098
02:44:01,254 --> 02:44:04,059
<i>at General Eisenhower's headquarters</i>

2099
02:44:05,093 --> 02:44:06,616
<i>General Jodl</i>

2100
02:44:07,677 --> 02:44:11,195
<i>signed the Act of Unconditional Surrender</i>

2101
02:44:11,784 --> 02:44:16,956
<i>of all German
land, sea and air forces in Europe</i>

2102
02:44:17,738 --> 02:44:20,182
<i>to the Allied Expeditionary Force</i>

2103
02:44:21,414 --> 02:44:25,343
<i>and simultaneously to the Soviet High Command.</i>

2104
02:44:26,138 --> 02:44:28,626
<i>The German war is therefore at an end.</i>

2105
02:44:29,854 --> 02:44:31,741
<i>But let us not forget for a moment...</i>

2106
02:44:31,815 --> 02:44:34,709
I think
it's time, the guards came into the factory.

2107
02:44:36,107 --> 02:44:37,955
<i>Japan, with all her treachery...</i>

2108
02:44:39,173 --> 02:44:41,485
The unconditional surrender of Germany

2109
02:44:41,909 --> 02:44:42,918
